<plot>Since the death of her son, Perle is nothing but a pale copy of herself. Hovering between dream and reality, she saunters in her lifeless apartment, burdened by an ordeal, the most difficult for a mother to bear. To overcome it, she digs within herself and her memories, thus working a first passage towards the promise of inner peace.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?429408</url></doc>
